	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think that a meele druid is just plain wrong. I play a warrior and on raids or grouped, if i ever saw a druid or cleric or caster trying to tank, i mean attempting to tank on every mob this would be a serious concern for me. I would most likely leave because this is something that leads to problems because people arent doing what their supposed to. I also have a bunch of low level chars that see this all the time and it just stresses the hell outta me. my druid is 50+ and his 1 hand slash is 30 and he even has the druid epic. so basically my point. <br><br>---------DRUIDS SHOULD NOT MEELE--------<br><br>Scthyx Level 60 Warrior -Veeshan-<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76371" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=76371</a><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
